Firstly, multiple text strings contained garbled characters which have been corrected to their proper German forms (e.g., 'Völcker-Historie', 'Grundsätze', '8vo.'). Secondly, the XML structure was invalid due to a nested <BIBL> tag, which has been corrected by making it a sibling element. Thirdly, several tags were incorrect or missing. A <PRIZE> tag was incorrectly used for what appears to be an author and has been changed to a new <BIBL> entry with an <AUTHOR> tag. Subtitles and descriptors were moved inside the appropriate <TITLE> tags. A missing <FORMAT> tag was added by separating it from the volume information. Finally, junk characters were removed and punctuation was placed correctly outside of the tags for better structure.
